      "review_summary": "This PR adds an optional `read.encoding` string to the built-in session read tool, decodes text buffers with `TextDecoder` or a Buffer fallback when supplied, updates `ReadToolInput`, and adds GBK/default UTF-8 tests.\n\nPR surface: Source +44, Tests +45. Total +89 across 3 files.\n\nReproducibility: yes. at source level: current main and the latest release decode the session read text path as UTF-8 only, and the linked issue's GBK byte sample mojibakes under that decode. I did not run a live Chinese Windows gateway session in this read-only review.",
